://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Martin-Shkreli-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/Martin-Shkreli-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马丁·什克雷利（Martin Shkreli）被命令放弃他的稀有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">武器氏族</a>专辑《曾在莎林林的一次》中的副本。</p><p>根据<a href="https://news.artnet.com/art-world/martin-shkreli-wu-tang-clan-album-copying-ruling-2527688"><em>Artnet</em></a>的说法，法官命令Skhreli在一周内推翻他拥有的任何副本，并于周五早上（8月23日）通过了该裁决。该判断<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-sued-for-copying-and-playing-wu-tang-clans-once-upon-a-time-in-shaolin-without-permission-3765468">源于数字艺术集体Pelerdao对Shkreli的起诉，要求在6月无允许的情况下复制和播放专辑</a>。</p><p>法官帕梅拉·陈（Pamela Chen）还要求什克雷利（Shkreli）提供誓章，以确认他的放弃，以及他制作的所有副本的清单，将其分配给的所有副本以及分配中的任何利润。 Shkreli被命令在30天内将此清单交给法官。</p><p> Shrekli的律师没有立即回应<em>Artnet</em>的置评请求。 </p><figure id="attachment_2738464" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2738464" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2738464" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482.jpg" alt="马丁·施克莱利" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GettyImages-826444482-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2738464" class="wp-caption-text"> Martin Shkreli信用：Drew Anger/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这位前对冲基金经理和“ Pharma-Bro”（Pharma-Bro） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rza-regrets-selling-wu-tang-clans-once-upon-a-time-in-shaolin-martin-shkreli-album-3081934">在205年以200万美元（140万英镑）购买了纪录的唯一副本</a>，并于去年6月被起诉非法直播专辑。</p><p> Shkreli在专辑直到2103年才能在2103年才能在聆听派对上播放的情况下购买了专辑。尽管受到限制，他还是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-plays-fabled-wu-tang-album-as-he-discusses-fraud-conviction-2122235">在2017年的一次直播中播放了专辑的片段</a>，然后试图在eBay上出售专辑。</p><p>尽管从未完成此次出售，但在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/martin-shkreli-found-guilty-fraud-2121196">定罪</a>后，Shkreli被迫交出这张专辑，当时有740万美元（580万英镑）的资产被联邦法院扣押。这张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkrelis-2million-wu-tang-clan-album-has-been-sold-by-the-us-government-3004668">现在掌握在数字艺术集体Pleasrdao的手中。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/martin-shkreli-ordered-to-surrender-his-copies-of-rare-wu-tang-clan-album-3787005">马丁·什克雷利（Martin Shkreli）的帖子下令放弃他的稀有武氏氏族专辑的副本，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
